      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BULL DURHAM (6) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at his last four runs. Last time finished 2nd in a Grade 5 on April 6 over 390m at Shepparton behind Rivia Umiko beaten a head (22.66). Overdue and expected to feature again. LIVIN' LAVISH (2) hit the ground running and on speed early but faded out of it to finish fifth (22.95) at this track over 400m. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from four starts. One of the better chances. SASSY GAL (4) missed the frame two back but wound up strongly last time, finishing on late when third (22.93) in a Grade 5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including four wins. Expected to feature. PAW VARNA (1) defied the market to win last start and cannot be ruled out.",
